data.description: Beautiful 4-bedroom, 3.5 bath custom home situated on a serene .4-acre lot with mature trees is ready for you to move in and make it your new home! The screened-in porch is the perfect spot to start your morning with a cup of coffee or a green smoothie.  The main floor has built-ins, hardwood & parquet floors, and crown molding. Formal dining room. Stunning kitchen with custom cabinets, SS appliances, center island, planning desk & pantry. The family room features built-in bookshelves, wood burning fireplace & custom brick feature floor. It is the perfect spot for spending cozy evenings with family & friends. With the second living space and large bedrooms there is plenty of room for everybody to spread out and could be the perfect set-up for a multi-generational family!  The spacious primary bedroom has an en-suite bathroom and custom-built closet.  The large backyard with mature trees and an invisible fence provides a great space to play with kids, dogs or plant a huge garden.  Mini-barn provides plenty of storage for lawn equipment and toys. Top it off with a 3-car garage and this could be your dream home!
